<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000603/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """The type of course and the approach described above make more convenient to select an assessment mechanism different to the traditional final exam. A continuous evaluation methodology is here proposed for this course, based on a set of short quizzes, or on a short project, or on both. This way, main concepts could be properly set up while the attractive of the contents are increased.
In the evaluation, an important weight has been given to laboratory practices, since this is considered a fundamental and distinct aspect of training in this type of discipline."""@es ;
